{"tid":148641,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"免費送 電繪畫版 有心畫電繪既巴絲來吧！","createTime":"2017-03-08T16:58:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-08T17:12:05.000Z","uid":39262,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7ad4b2df7cdf7a2a7de1fba2dd36ebcaa2638349","tid":148641,"uid":39262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:58:16.000Z","msg":"呢個用左3年幾左右，唔係成日用，70%新<br />\n有筆有筆芯跟埋，隻安裝碟都有<br />\n因為唔習慣要望電腦mon又要對準個板黎畫<br />\n存左好耐錢買到個液晶繪圖板，<br />\n咁呢個入門級既板可以安心上路啦!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢啲濕鳩2手野賣出去，實賣唔出，掉左又浪費<br />\n所以想送比有心畫電繪既巴絲<br />\n<br />\n可以既話聽日樂富4:30左右送出<br />\n只限樂富<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/09/004455_7f4876b7e490de2046dd67b56a7b27ca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F09%2F004455_7f4876b7e490de2046dd67b56a7b27ca.jpg&h=baa6a2f2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e766dca3043448d109f570f90ab5269441a4b0c4","tid":148641,"uid":39262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:59:02.000Z","msg":"可留底email聯絡"},{"pid":"4ae5201b81e12b9fa3fb36750d3d3d8d99e85f91","tid":148641,"uid":55564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T17:00:54.000Z","msg":"想要 不過430上緊堂 無緣"},{"pid":"2b9bf4191f2ca84129db715bc34769b2edf88a5e","tid":148641,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T17:01:28.000Z","msg":"聽日黎拎ok?"},{"pid":"7d717a6fd5b3b2fdaba29c94d7657bde37bbdb72","tid":148641,"uid":50112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T17:01:51.000Z","msg":"有興趣<br />\nTg Peiwest26"},{"pid":"8f5677b56070b075a6b888610947428adb950f33","tid":148641,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime